# Skeleton 骨架屏

> 加载中结构提示，避免内容跳动。  
> **状态**：Beta


## Demo
::TuffDemo{title="Skeleton" description="文本与头像混合占位" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TxSkeleton :loading="true" :lines="3" />
    <TxSkeleton variant="circle" :width="40" :height="40" />
  </template>
---
#preview
<div class="tuff-demo-row">
  <tx-skeleton :loading="true" :lines="3" />
  <tx-skeleton variant="circle" :width="40" :height="40" />
</div>
::

## API（简版）
::TuffPropsTable
---
rows:
  - name: loading
    type: 'boolean'
    default: 'true'
    description: '是否显示骨架'
  - name: lines
    type: 'number'
    default: '3'
    description: '文本行数'
  - name: variant
    type: "'line' | 'circle'"
    default: 'line'
    description: '形状'
---
::

